      "dateCreated": "2026-04-01",
      "description": "A Snakemake pipeline that performs differential expression analysis on Salmon-quantified Bulk RNA-seq data using edgeR (TMM/quasi-likelihood), followed by downstream functional enrichment analyses including GO over-representation, GSEA, Reactome pathway analysis, and Hallmark gene-set scoring. Outputs include DEG Excel tables, volcano plots, and enrichment plots.",
